name: MINT Income Fund
longDescription: The Investment objective of MINT Income fund are to provide monthly distribution and to enhance long term return through capital appreciation. The fund seek to achieve its investment objective by diligently selecting and actively managing a diversified portfolio comprised primarily of equity income securities across a broad range of industries and geographic regions.
